‹w ›      - Word
‹W ›      - Word (space-separated)
‹' ›      - Single quotes
‹" ›      - Double quotes
‹( ›      - Parentheses
‹[ ›      - Brackets
‹{ ›      - Braces
‹t ›      - Tag (html/xml)
‹s ›      - Sentence
‹p ›      - Paragraph

=h= Operators

