Case operators should repeat only last symbol, e.g. ‹g~~ ›changes case of the current line.

‹›         Editing:
‹d ›       - Delete (cut)
‹c ›       - Change (delete + enter insert mode)
‹y ›       - Yank (copy)

‹›         Indent:
‹> ›       - Increase
‹< ›       - Decrease

‹›         Change case:
‹g~ ›      - Toggle
‹gU ›      - Uppercase
‹gu ›      - Lowercase

‹›         Other:
‹= ›       - Auto-indent
‹! ›       - Filter text through external command

